Description:
You reach the Ulminin Obelisk, but because of the sand you are too high.

Although you can see the Glyph, the runes that would allow you to advance are still many meters below you.

You try to make your way through the sand, but after removing a thin layer of sand, it solidifies. You get the impression that there is a chamber under the sand.
DescriptionAction: There is nothing else you can do here, now you have to find a way to access the lower chambers to read the runes on the obelisk.
